iz Gloria</span>旋转餐厅用餐，同时欣赏群峰美景静静划过眼前。<span><br />   </span>除了冬季滑雪，夏季您还可以在这里徒步旅行。</span></p><p><span style="font-size:12px;font-family:''宋体'';">北坡徒步小径：<span><br />   </span>路线：<span>Mürren - Spielbodenalp - Schiltalp - Blumental –   Allmendhubel <br />   </span>单程<span>2</span>小时<span>30</span>分钟<span><br />   </span>该路线最大特色为沿途欣赏伯尔尼高地阿尔卑斯山北坡的震撼美景。沿途设有<span>12</span>个信息指示牌。需穿户外鞋。</span></p><p><span style="font-size:12px;font-family:''宋体'';">山景小径<span><br />   </span>路线：<span>Allmendhubel - Dorenhubel – Grütschalp<br />   </span>单程<span>1</span>小时<span>30</span>分钟<span><br />   </span>欣赏艾格峰、僧侣峰和少女峰</span></p></td><td width="314" valign="top" style="width:314px;border-top-style:none;border-left-style:none;border-bottom-width:1px;border-bottom-color:#000000;border-right-width:1px;border-right-color:#000000;padding:0 7px;"><p><img src="/opentrip/Public/Uploads/desc/2016-06/22/14665923877051.jpg" alt="14665923877051.jpg" style="width:141px;height:89px;" /></p><p><img src="/opentrip/Public/Uploads/desc/2016-06/22/146659238949.jpg" style="width:0px;height:0px;" alt="146659238949.jpg" /></p><p><img src="/opentrip/Public/Uploads/desc/2016-06/22/14665924267963.jpg" alt="14665924267963.jpg" style="width:140px;height:89px;" /></p></td></tr><tr><td width="33" valign="top" style="width:33px;border-right-width:1px;border-bottom-width:1px;border-left-width:1px;border-right-color:#000000;border-bottom-color:#000000;border-left-color:#000000;border-top-style:none;padding:0 7px;"><p><span>D5</span></p></td><td width="60" valign="top" style="width:60px;border-top-style:none;border-left-style:none;border-bottom-width:1px;border-bottom-color:#000000;border-right-width:1px;border-right-color:#000000;padding:0 7px;"><p><span style="font-family:''宋体'';">巴士</span></p><p><span style="font-family:''宋体'';">直升</span></p><p><span style="font-family:''宋体'';">飞机</span></p></td><td width="312" valign="top" style="width:312px;border-top-style:none;border-left-style:none;border-bottom-width:1px;border-